  "texts": [
    "IntroductionIn the last years, Artificial Intelligence (AI) has shown great promise in improving or revolutionizing various fields of research and practice, including knowledge engineering.",
    "The recent big leap in AI-based assistant chatbots, like Chat-GPT (Generative Pre-trained Transformer) model, has created new opportunities to automate knowledge engineering tasks and reduce the workload on human experts.",
    "With the growing volume of information in different fields, the need for scalable and efficient methods to manage and extract knowledge from data that also adapt to new sources is critical.",
    "Despite the advances in research w.r.t.",
    "(semi)automation, knowledge engineering tasks still rely vastly on human experts."
  ],
